### Get global leaderboard (all-time)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/leaderboards/global

### Get global leaderboard (monthly)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/leaderboards/global?period=monthly

### Get category leaderboard (science)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/leaderboards/categories/science

### Get user rank (requires auth)
# Assume you have a valid JWT token or session cookie
GET http://localhost:3000/api/leaderboards/users/me/rank
Authorization: Bearer <your_actual_jwt_token_here>
